d bonds", "bbox": [100.3, 443.3, 567.0, 471.2]}, {"text": "In certain situations, Tyco guaranteed Flow Control’s performance to third parties or provided financial guarantees for", "bbox": [100.3, 468.1, 1142.5, 496.2]}, {"text": "financial commitments of Flow Control. In situations where Flow Control and Tyco were unable to obtain a release from", "bbox": [100.3, 493.2, 1142.6, 521.2]}, {"text": "these guarantees in connection with the spin-off of Flow Control from Tyco, we will indemnify Tyco for any losses it suffers", "bbox": [100.3, 518.2, 1142.6, 546.2]}, {"text": "as a result of such guarantees.", "bbox": [100.3, 543.2, 352.6, 571.2]}, {"text": "In disposing of assets or businesses, we often provide representations, warranties and indemnities to cover various risks", "bbox": [100.3, 580.7, 1142.6, 608.7]}, {"text": "including unknown damage to the assets, environmental risks involved in the sale of real estate, liability to investigate and", "bbox": [100.3, 605.7, 1142.7, 633.8]}, {"text": "remediate environmental contamination at waste disposal sites and manufacturing facilities and unidentified tax liabilities", "bbox": [100.3, 630.7, 1142.5, 658.8]}, {"text": "and legal fees related to periods prior to disposition. We do not have the ability to reasonably estimate the potential liability", "bbox": [100.3, 655.7, 1142.7, 683.8]}, {"text": "due to the inchoate and unknown nature of these potential liabilities. However, we have no reason to believe that these", "bbox": [100.3, 680.7, 1142.6, 708.8]}, {"text": "uncertainties would have a material adverse effect on our financial position, results of operations or cash flows.", "bbox": [100.3, 705.7, 1040.2, 733.8]}, {"text": "In the ordinary course of business, we are required to commit to bonds, letters of credit and bank guarantees that require", "bbox": [100.3, 743.2, 1142.5, 771.3]}, {"text": "payments to our customers for any non-performance. The outstanding face value of these instruments fluctuates with the", "bbox": [100.3, 768.2, 1142.5, 796.3]}, {"text": "value of our projects in process and in our backlog. In addition, we issue financial stand-by letters of credit primarily to", "bbox": [100.3, 793.2, 1142.5, 821.3]}, {"text": "secure our performance to third parties under self-insurance programs.", "bbox": [100.3, 818.2, 699.3, 846.3]}, {"text": "As of December 31, 2016 and 2015, the outstanding value of bonds, letters of credit and bank guarantees totaled $331.0 million", "bbox": [100.3, 855.7, 1142.7, 883.8]}, {"text": "and $402.2 million, respectively, of which $156.6 million and $202.3 million, respectively, relate to the Valves & Controls", "bbox": [100.3, 880.7, 1142.5, 908.8]}, {"text": "business classified as held for sale.", "bbox": [100.3, 905.8, 392.5, 933.8]}, {"text": "18.", "bbox": [100.3, 955.4, 131.4, 984.3]}, {"text": "Selected Quarterly Data (Unaudited)", "bbox": [171.2, 955.4, 508.0, 984.3]}, {"text": "The following tables present 2016 and 2015 quarterly financial information:", "bbox": [100.3, 980.8, 738.4, 1008.8]}, {"text": "2016", "bbox": [824.4, 1021.3, 864.9, 1050.2]}, {"text": "In millions, except per-share data", "bbox": [106.7, 1073.0, 391.6, 1100.7]}, {"text": "First", "bbox": [582.3, 1047.3, 626.2, 1076.1]}, {"text": "Quarter", "bbox": [567.4, 1072.3, 641.2, 1101.1]}, {"text": "Second", "bbox": [692.4, 1047.3, 756.5, 1076.1]}, {"text": "Quarter", "bbox": [687.6, 1072.3, 761.4, 1101.1]}, {"text": "Third", "bbox": [818.1, 1047.3, 871.2, 1076.1]}, {"text": "Quarter", "bbox": [807.8, 1072.3, 881.6, 1101.1]}, {"text": "Fourth", "bbox": [933.6, 1047.3, 996.1, 1076.1]}, {"text": "Quarter", "bbox": [928.0, 1072.3, 1001.8, 1101.1]}, {"text": "Full", "bbox": [1066.6, 1047.3, 1103.6, 1076.1]}, {"text": "Year", "bbox": [1063.8, 1072.3, 1106.4, 1101.1]}, {"text": "Net sales", "bbox": [106.7, 1098.9, 182.7, 1126.9]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [559.0, 1098.9, 569.4, 1126.9]}, {"text": "1,190.0", "bbox": [587.1, 1098.9, 649.6, 1126.9]}, {"text": "$",